---
---

<html lang="en" data-theme="dark">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EyeMia — Open-Source Eye Gaze Communication System</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="EyeMia is an open-source eye gaze communication system for people with Rett Syndrome, ALS, cerebral palsy, and other conditions that affect motor control."
    />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" />
    <style is:inline>
      :root {
        --primary: #2A7FBF;
        --deep: #1B4F7A;
        --light: #6DB3E0;
        --accent: #C8982A;
        --error: #B53030;
        --success: #3A8F5C;
        --muted: #6B6B78;
        --bg: #1a1a22;
        --bg-card: #22222c;
        --bg-code: #1e1e28;
        --text: #e4e4ea;
        --text-secondary: #9d9da8;
        --text-muted: #6B6B78;
        --border: #2e2e3a;
        --border-hover: #3e3e4e;
      }
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      body {
        font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.65; font-size: 15px;
      }
      .topnav {
        position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 56px;
        background: #16161e; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0 24px; z-index: 100;
      }
      .topnav-logo {
        display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
        text-decoration: none; color: var(--text);
        font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-right: 32px;
      }
      .logo-icon {
        width: 28px; height: 28px; background: var(--primary);
        border-radius: 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      }
      .logo-icon::after {
        content: ''; width: 12px; height: 12px;
        background: var(--accent); border-radius: 2px; transform: rotate(45deg);
      }
      .topnav-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: center; }
      .topnav-link {
        color: var(--text-secondary); text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 500; transition: color 0.15s;
      }
      .topnav-link:hover { color: var(--text); }
      .topnav-link.active { color: var(--primary); }
      .topnav-right { margin-left: auto; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; }
      .gh-link { color: var(--text-secondary); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500; }
      .gh-link:hover { color: var(--text); }
      .license-badge {
        font-size: 0.68rem; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 4px;
        background: rgba(58,143,92,0.15); color: var(--success); font-weight: 600;
      }
      .hero {
        padding: 120px 24px 60px; text-align: center;
        position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      }
      .hero::before {
        content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
        background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(200,152,42,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
        pointer-events: none;
      }
      .hero-badge {
        display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
        padding: 4px 14px; border-radius: 20px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(200,152,42,0.3);
        font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .hero-badge .dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); }
      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 3.4rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 16px; max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;
      }
      .hero .tagline {
        font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-secondary);
        max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 32px; line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }
      .btn {
        display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
        padding: 11px 24px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.92rem;
        font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.15s;
      }
      .btn-primary { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--accent); }
      .btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.9; }
      .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
      .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--border-hover); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }
      .section { padding: 80px 24px; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
      .section-label {
        font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 8px;
      }
      .section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 8px; }
      .section .section-desc {
        font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-secondary);
        max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 36px; line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .callout {
        border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 18px; margin: 0 auto 40px;
        font-size: 0.95rem; display: flex; gap: 10px; max-width: 800px;
        background: rgba(200,152,42,0.08); border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
        color: var(--text-secondary);
      }
      .diff-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
      .diff-card {
        background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; transition: border-color 0.15s;
      }
      .diff-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-hover); }
      .diff-icon {
        width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 10px;
        display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      .diff-card h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; }
      .diff-card p { font-size: 0.86rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.55; }
      .cap-grid {
        display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 14px;
        max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: left;
      }
      .cap-card {
        background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px 18px;
      }
      .cap-title {
        font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 4px;
      }
      .cap-desc { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
      .arch-visual { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; }
      .arch-layer {
        padding: 18px 24px; border-radius: 10px;
        text-align: center; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem;
      }
      .arch-layer .desc { font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: 0.8; margin-top: 3px; }
      .arch-arrow { text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 2px 0; }
      .arch-caption { text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.82rem; margin-top: 20px; }
      .status-badge {
        display: inline-block; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;
        background: rgba(200,152,42,0.15); color: var(--accent);
      }
      .cta { text-align: center; padding: 80px 24px; }
      .cta h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
      .cta p {
        color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.05rem;
        margin-bottom: 28px; max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;
      }
      .footer {
        padding: 32px 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.82rem;
      }
      .footer a { color: var(--text-secondary); text-decoration: none; }
      .footer a:hover { color: var(--text); }
      .footer-links { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .diff-grid, .cap-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav class="topnav">
      <a href="/" class="topnav-logo">
        <div class="logo-icon"></div>
        mosaigo
      </a>
      <div class="topnav-links">
        <a href="/getting-started/" class="topnav-link">Docs</a>
        <a href="/mosoptics/" class="topnav-link">mosoptics</a>
        <a href="/eyemia/" class="topnav-link active">EyeMia</a>
      </div>
      <div class="topnav-right">
        <a href="https://github.com/mosaigoio/eyemia" class="gh-link">GitHub</a>
        <span class="license-badge">Apache-2.0</span>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-badge"><span class="dot"></span> Open source &middot; Apache-2.0 &middot; Pre-release</div>
      <h1>Every eye tells a <span style="color:var(--accent);">story</span></h1>
      <p class="tagline">EyeMia is an open-source eye gaze communication system for people with Rett Syndrome, ALS, cerebral palsy, and other conditions that affect motor control. Your eyes become your voice.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/eyemia/" class="btn btn-primary">Read the Docs</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/mosaigoio/eyemia" class="btn btn-secondary">View on GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="callout">
        <span style="font-size:1.3rem;">&#9829;</span>
        <div><strong>Why this exists:</strong> Rett Syndrome affects ~1 in 10,000 girls, taking away speech and hand use while leaving cognitive ability intact. Eye gaze is their voice. Commercial eye-tracking systems cost $10,000+ and lock families into proprietary ecosystems. EyeMia aims to make eye gaze communication accessible, affordable, and open to everyone.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="section-label">The vision</div>
      <h2>Communication is a right, not a luxury</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Individuals with severe motor disabilities rely on assistive technology to communicate. EyeMia provides an open-source alternative that puts families and caregivers in control.</p>
      <div class="diff-grid">
        <div class="diff-card">
          <div class="diff-icon" style="background:rgba(200,152,42,0.12);color:var(--accent);">&#128483;</div>
          <h3>For Non-Verbal People</h3>
          <p>Communicate needs, wants, and feelings through eye gaze. Select symbols, words, and phrases by looking at them. Generate speech from selections. Engage with the world through your eyes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="diff-card">
          <div class="diff-icon" style="background:rgba(42,127,191,0.12);color:var(--primary);">&#128101;</div>
          <h3>For Caregivers &amp; Family</h3>
          <p>Understand what your loved one needs. Configure communication boards, adjust sensitivity, track usage patterns. A caregiver app gives control without technical expertise.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="diff-card">
          <div class="diff-icon" style="background:rgba(109,179,224,0.12);color:var(--light);">&#127891;</div>
          <h3>For Teachers &amp; Therapists</h3>
          <p>Customize symbol grids for learning objectives. Track dwell time patterns to understand attention and progress. Integrate into classroom routines with a dedicated device.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="diff-card">
          <div class="diff-icon" style="background:rgba(58,143,92,0.12);color:var(--success);">&#128161;</div>
          <h3>Open Source &amp; Affordable</h3>
          <p>No $10,000 proprietary device. Run on low-power edge hardware with dual USB cameras and a touchscreen. Open source means anyone can improve, adapt, and share it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" style="text-align:center;">
      <div class="section-label">Capabilities</div>
      <h2>What EyeMia will do</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">A complete eye gaze communication system — from camera to speech — running on affordable edge hardware.</p>
      <div class="cap-grid">
        <div class="cap-card">
          <div class="cap-title">Real-Time Gaze Tracking</div>
          <div class="cap-desc">Dual camera gaze detection with precision and jitter smoothing in high and low light conditions</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cap-card">
          <div class="cap-title">Text-to-Speech</div>
          <div class="cap-desc">Vocalize selected symbols, words, and sentences — turning gaze selections into spoken communication</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cap-card">
          <div class="cap-title">Face Recognition</div>
          <div class="cap-desc">Recognize registered users to personalize communication boards and greetings</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cap-card">
          <div class="cap-title">Head &amp; Movement Tracking</div>
          <div class="cap-desc">Detect head position and stereotypic movements, alert on seizures based on facial gestures</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cap-card">
          <div class="cap-title">AI Image Generation</div>
          <div class="cap-desc">Generate vibrant images associated with word meanings for engaging communication boards</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cap-card">
          <div class="cap-title">Adaptive Calibration</div>
          <div class="cap-desc">One-time calibration that adapts over time as the system learns the user's gaze patterns</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" style="text-align:center;">
      <div class="section-label">Architecture</div>
      <h2>Three layers, clear boundaries</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">EyeMia is built on mosaigo and mosoptics. The gaze pipeline runs on edge hardware, the overlay renders the communication UI, and the caretaker app provides remote control.</p>
      <div class="arch-visual">
        <div class="arch-layer" style="background:rgba(200,152,42,0.15);color:var(--accent);border:1px solid rgba(200,152,42,0.3);">
          EyeMia Client <span class="desc">— Overlay UI + Caretaker app (communication, calibration, settings)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="arch-arrow">controls &#8595;</div>
        <div class="arch-layer" style="background:rgba(42,127,191,0.15);color:var(--primary);border:1px solid rgba(42,127,191,0.3);">
          mosoptics <span class="desc">— Gaze pipeline (cam, face, eye, gaze, stereo — real-time on device)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="arch-arrow">built on &#8595;</div>
        <div class="arch-layer" style="background:rgba(27,79,122,0.3);color:var(--light);border:1px solid rgba(27,79,122,0.5);">
          mosaigo <span class="desc">— Engine, pipeline, typed steps, topics, config, validation</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="arch-caption">The overlay renders on a dedicated display. The caretaker app connects over the local network. All gaze processing happens on-device — no cloud dependency.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section" style="text-align:center;">
      <div class="section-label">Project status</div>
      <h2>Where we are</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">
        EyeMia is in active early development. The core pipeline framework (mosaigo) and vision library (mosoptics) are being built first.
      </p>
      <div class="status-badge">Pre-release &middot; Active Development</div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
      <h2>Help build the future of accessible communication</h2>
      <p>EyeMia is open source and welcomes contributors. Whether you're a developer, therapist, caregiver, or researcher — there's a place for you.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/eyemia/" class="btn btn-primary">Read the Docs</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/mosaigoio/eyemia" class="btn btn-secondary">View on GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="/">mosaigo</a>
        <a href="/eyemia/">Docs</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/mosaigoio/eyemia">GitHub</a>
      </div>
      <p>Apache-2.0 License &middot; Part of the <a href="/">mosaigoio</a> family</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
